name: 莉·巴韦尔
introduction: Leigh Barwell Is an actress and writer, known for her role as Tracey in the movie English Dogs in Bangkok and Rose in Bet Dead Casino. She has also had roles in The Prince and Me, Netflix movie Kate, United Six and ITV'S The Singapore Grip. She was born in Cambridge, England. As a teenager Leigh trained as a dancer for 4 years in the UK and after graduating she traveled extensively worldwide with her work, performing in many dance and musical style shows. She also choreographed for the movie Shanghai starring John Cusack.
